Package com.greystripe.sdk

Interface Summary
GSAd An interface that all ads implement.
GSAdListener An interface for listeners who want to be notified of ad receipt, clicks, and dismissals.
 

Class Summary
AdPosition Represents an immutable ad position after onAdResized() is called.
GSFullscreenActivity This class is not meant to be explicitly called by the developer.
GSFullscreenAd Instantiate this class to create a fullscreen ad that you can fetch, display, etc.
GSLeaderboardAdView This is the ad view for a 728x90 leaderboard banner ad.
GSMediumRectangleAdView This is the ad view for a 300x250 medium rectangle banner ad.
GSMobileBannerAdView This is the ad view for small 320x50 banner ads.
GSSdkInfo This class provides a place to store static data that is global to the SDK.
 

Enum Summary
GSAdErrorCode An enumeration of error codes the SDK uses when an ad fails.
